Class PrivateDataProviderListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, PrivateDataProviderListener, ProviderListener

    public abstract class PrivateDataProviderListenerAdapter
extends ProviderListenerAdapter
implements PrivateDataProviderListener
    An adapter which is notified of receipt of platform specific provider information. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
